<div id="Layer1" style="position:absolute; visibility: hidden; left:120px; top:180px; width:280px; height:320px"> <table width="100%" height="320" border="0"><tr> <td height="300" colspan="2"> <p align="left"><font class="atitulohistoria"><b> A Galinha Perdida</b></font></p><p align="left"><font class="anomeautores"><b> Ant&oacute;nio Torrado</b></font><br><font class="aprofissao"><b>escreveu</b></font></p><p align="left"><font class="anomeilustrador"> <b>Cristina Malaquias</b></font><br><font class="aprofissao"><b>ilustrou</b></font></p></td></tr><tr> <td width="50%" height="20">&nbsp;</td><td width="50%"> <img align="right" border="0" src="../../../images/Avancar.jpg" onClick="MM_showHideLayers('Layer2','','show');MM_showHideLayers('Layer1','','hide')" width="20" height="20"></td></tr></table></div><div id="Layer2" style="position:absolute; visibility: hidden; left:120px; top:180px; width:280px; height:320px"> <table width="100%" height="320" border="0"><tr> <td height="300" colspan="2" valign="top"> <font size="3" face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" color="#666666"><b> <div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">Esta galinha tinha-se distra&iacute;do e avan&ccedil;ara para longe do p&aacute;tio do quintal. Bica aqui, bica acol&aacute;, &agrave; cata do escaravelho cascudo ou da minhoca tenra, perdera-se das companheiras e ai que desceu a noite.
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">Por prud&ecirc;ncia, n&atilde;o se aventurou por descaminhos, ao calhar, apesar de a Lua prometer boa companhia.</div></b> </font> </td></tr><tr> <td width="50%" height="20"> <img align="left" border="0" src="../../../images/voltar.jpg" onClick="MM_showHideLayers('Layer2','','hide');MM_showHideLayers('Layer1','','show')" width="20" height="20"></td><td width="65%"> <img align="right" src="../../../images/Avancar.jpg" border="0" onClick="MM_showHideLayers('Layer3','','show');MM_showHideLayers('Layer2','','hide')" width="20" height="20"></td></tr></table></div><div id="Layer3" style="position:absolute; visibility: hidden; left:120px; top:180px; width:280px; height:320px"> <table width="100%" height="320" border="0"><tr> <td height="300" colspan="2" valign="top"> <font size="3" face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" color="#666666"><b> <div align="normal" style="line-height: 150%">
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">- Mais depressa chegarei amanh&atilde;, &agrave; primeira luz do <A class="alink" href="#" onMouseOver="stm(Text[17],Style[0])" onMouseOut="htm()">alvorecer</a> - disse de si para si a galinha. - Ainda se tivesse pintos &agrave; minha espera, arriscava, mas como os &uacute;ltimos que tive j&aacute; cantam de galo, n&atilde;o me ralo.</div></b> </font> </td></tr><tr> <td width="50%" height="20"> <img align="left" border="0" src="../../../images/voltar.jpg" onClick="MM_showHideLayers('Layer3','','hide');MM_showHideLayers('Layer2','','show')" width="20" height="20"></td><td width="65%"> <img align="right" src="../../../images/Avancar.jpg" border="0" onClick="MM_showHideLayers('Layer4','','show');MM_showHideLayers('Layer3','','hide')" width="20" height="20"></td></tr></table></div><div id="Layer4" style="position:absolute; visibility: hidden; left:120px; top:180px; width:280px; height:320px"> <table width="100%" height="320" border="0"><tr> <td height="300" colspan="2" valign="top"> <font size="3" face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" color="#666666"><b> <div align="normal" style="line-height: 150%">
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">Procurou poleiro num ramo alto de uma &aacute;rvore e, l&aacute; chegada, aninhou-se, nem que estivesse em casa.
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">Ela a fechar os olhos de sono, quando sentiu uma <A class="alink" href="#" onMouseOver="stm(Text[18],Style[0])" onMouseOut="htm()">restolhada</a>, na base do tronco. Por prud&ecirc;ncia, saltou para um ramo mais acima e esperou, de olhinho alerta.</div></b> </font> </td></tr><tr> <td width="50%" height="20"> <img align="left" border="0" src="../../../images/voltar.jpg" onClick="MM_showHideLayers('Layer4','','hide');MM_showHideLayers('Layer3','','show')" width="20" height="20"></td><td width="65%"> <img align="right" src="../../../images/Avancar.jpg" border="0" onClick="MM_showHideLayers('Layer5','','show');MM_showHideLayers('Layer4','','hide')" width="20" height="20"></td></tr></table></div><div id="Layer5" style="position:absolute; visibility: hidden; left:120px; top:180px; width:280px; height:320px"> <table width="100%" height="320" border="0"><tr> <td height="300" colspan="2" valign="top"> <font size="3" face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" color="#666666"><b> <div align="normal" style="line-height: 150%">
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">Era a raposa, que farejava presa de apetite.
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">- Senhora galinha, onde est&aacute; que n&atilde;o a <A class="alink" href="#" onMouseOver="stm(Text[19],Style[0])" onMouseOut="htm()">enxergo</a>?
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">- Estou onde estou e bem muito obrigada - respondeu a galinha, que n&atilde;o estava para conversas.
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">- O seu estado p&otilde;e-me em cuidado - persistia a velhaca.</div></b> </font> </td></tr><tr> <td width="50%" height="20"> <img align="left" border="0" src="../../../images/voltar.jpg" onClick="MM_showHideLayers('Layer5','','hide');MM_showHideLayers('Layer4','','show')" width="20" height="20"></td><td width="65%"> <img align="right" src="../../../images/Avancar.jpg" border="0" onClick="MM_showHideLayers('Layer6','','show');MM_showHideLayers('Layer5','','hide')" width="20" height="20"></td></tr></table></div><div id="Layer6" style="position:absolute; visibility: hidden; left:120px; top:180px; width:280px; height:320px"> <table width="100%" height="320" border="0"><tr> <td height="300" colspan="2" valign="top"> <font size="3" face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" color="#666666"><b> <div align="normal" style="line-height: 150%"> - Com esta aragem da noite, ainda apanha um resfriamento.
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">- N&atilde;o se preocupe e v&aacute; &agrave; sua vida, senhora raposa.
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">- Preocupo-me e muito. Anda tanta humidade no ar, que n&atilde;o h&aacute; melhor abrigo do que a capoeira. Quer que lhe indique o caminho?
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">A galinha nem respondeu.</div></b> </font> </td></tr><tr> <td width="50%" height="20"> <img align="left" border="0" src="../../../images/voltar.jpg" onClick="MM_showHideLayers('Layer6','','hide');MM_showHideLayers('Layer5','','show')" width="20" height="20"></td><td width="65%"> <img align="right" src="../../../images/Avancar.jpg" border="0" onClick="MM_showHideLayers('Layer7','','show');MM_showHideLayers('Layer6','','hide')" width="20" height="20"></td></tr></table></div><div id="Layer7" style="position:absolute; visibility: hidden; left:120px; top:180px; width:280px; height:320px"> <table width="100%" height="320" border="0"><tr> <td height="300" colspan="2" valign="top"> <font size="3" face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" color="#666666"><b> <div align="normal" style="line-height: 150%"> Teimava a raposa:
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">- Al&eacute;m do mais h&aacute; o perigo das cobras... Se fosse a si descia donde est&aacute;.
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">A galinha nem tugiu.
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">- O que mais me aflige &eacute; a sua sa&uacute;de. A&iacute; em cima, parada ao frio, constipa-se, engripa-se, ganha febre... N&atilde;o ter&aacute; j&aacute;?</div></b> </font> </td></tr><tr> <td width="50%" height="20"> <img align="left" border="0" src="../../../images/voltar.jpg" onClick="MM_showHideLayers('Layer7','','hide');MM_showHideLayers('Layer6','','show')" width="20" height="20"></td><td width="65%"> <img align="right" src="../../../images/Avancar.jpg" border="0" onClick="MM_showHideLayers('Layer8','','show');MM_showHideLayers('Layer7','','hide')" width="20" height="20"></td></tr></table></div><div id="Layer8" style="position:absolute; visibility: hidden; left:120px; top:180px; width:280px; height:320px"> <table width="100%" height="320" border="0"><tr> <td height="300" colspan="2" valign="top"> <font size="3" face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" color="#666666"><b> <div align="normal" style="line-height: 150%">
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">- Sou capaz de ter - disse a galinha, s&oacute; para dizer qualquer coisa.
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">- Ent&atilde;o des&ccedil;a que eu lhe tiro a temperatura e ausculto e examino a garganta. Tenho estudos de medicina veterin&aacute;ria, n&atilde;o sabia?</div></b> </font> </td></tr><tr> <td width="50%" height="20"> <img align="left" border="0" src="../../../images/voltar.jpg" onClick="MM_showHideLayers('Layer8','','hide');MM_showHideLayers('Layer7','','show')" width="20" height="20"></td><td width="65%"> <img align="right" src="../../../images/Avancar.jpg" border="0" onClick="MM_showHideLayers('Layer9','','show');MM_showHideLayers('Layer8','','hide')" width="20" height="20"></td></tr></table></div><div id="Layer9" style="position:absolute; visibility: hidden; left:120px; top:180px; width:280px; height:320px"> <table width="100%" height="320" border="0"><tr> <td height="300" colspan="2" valign="top"> <font size="3" face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" color="#666666"><b> <div align="normal" style="line-height: 150%">
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">- Desculpe, senhora raposa, mas eu s&oacute; me consulto com o meu m&eacute;dico - disse a galinha, rindo-se por dentro.
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">- E quem &eacute; que a assiste, pode-se saber?
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">- &Eacute; o Fiel, o c&atilde;o da quinta, que eu mandei chamar e est&aacute; a&iacute; n&atilde;o tarda.</div></b> </font> </td></tr><tr> <td width="50%" height="20"> <img align="left" border="0" src="../../../images/voltar.jpg" onClick="MM_showHideLayers('Layer9','','hide');MM_showHideLayers('Layer8','','show')" width="20" height="20"></td><td width="65%"> <img align="right" src="../../../images/Avancar.jpg" border="0" onClick="MM_showHideLayers('Layer10','','show');MM_showHideLayers('Layer9','','hide')" width="20" height="20"></td></tr></table></div><div id="Layer10" style="position:absolute; visibility: hidden; left:120px; top:180px; width:280px; height:320px"> <table width="100%" height="320" border="0"><tr> <td height="300" colspan="2" valign="top"> <font size="3" face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" color="#666666"><b> <div align="normal" style="line-height: 150%">
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">A raposa alarmou-se:
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">- E ele vir&aacute;?
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">- J&aacute; o oi&ccedil;o - disse a galinha.
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">- Sendo assim, vou-me embora eu, que n&atilde;o gosto de fazer concorr&ecirc;ncia a colegas de profiss&atilde;o.
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">E a raposa fugiu, de rabo entre as pernas.</div></b> </font> </td></tr><tr> <td width="50%" height="20"> <img align="left" border="0" src="../../../images/voltar.jpg" onClick="MM_showHideLayers('Layer10','','hide');MM_showHideLayers('Layer9','','show')" width="20" height="20"></td><td width="65%"> <img align="right" src="../../../images/Avancar.jpg" border="0" onClick="MM_showHideLayers('Layer11','','show');MM_showHideLayers('Layer10','','hide')" width="20" height="20"></td></tr></table></div><div id="Layer11" style="position:absolute; visibility: hidden; left:120px; top:180px; width:280px; height:320px"> <table width="100%" height="320" border="0"><tr> <td height="300" colspan="2" valign="top"> <font size="3" face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" color="#666666"><b> <div align="normal" style="line-height: 150%">
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">Mais sossegada, a galinha escondeu a cabe&ccedil;a na asa e adormeceu. Nem sempre a raposa &eacute; a mais matreira...</div></b> </font> </td></tr><tr> <td width="50%" height="20"> <img align="left" border="0" src="../../../images/voltar.jpg" onClick="MM_showHideLayers('Layer11','','hide');MM_showHideLayers('Layer10','','show')" width="20" height="20"></td><td width="35%"><a href="imprimir.pdf" target="_blank"> <img src="../../../images/impre.jpg" align="left" border="0" width="20" height="20"></a><a href="javascript:MM_openBrWindow('../../../pop_votar.aspx?Mes=10&Dia=14','','menubar=no,width=270,height=170')"><img src="../../../images/votar_over.gif" align="right" border="0" width="67" height="20"></a></td></tr></table></div> 
